#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:54 cd72a9667fcd47b088f2443602edbd20
msgid "生成音频总线布局"
msgstr "Audio bus."

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:56 8dd263f19901498bbf2246c579e2879f
msgid ""
"这将扫描 Godot 的 `AudioServer`_ 总线层级并创建对应的 "
":ref:`FmodAudioBusLayout<FmodAudioBusLayout>` 和 "
":ref:`FmodAudioBus<FmodAudioBus>` 实例，以确保 FMOD 的总线结构与 Godot 的总线结构同步。"
msgstr "Scans the Godot `AudioServer`_ bus hierarchy and creates matching :ref:`FmodAudioBusLayout<FmodAudioBusLayout>` and :ref:`FmodAudioBus<FmodAudioBus>` instances so the FMOD bus structure stays synchronized with Godot's bus structure."

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:61 054d19d973b54c59ac97862588216fc3
msgid ""
":ref:`FmodAudioBusLayout<FmodAudioBusLayout>` get_audio_bus_layout() "
"static"
msgstr ""
":ref:`FmodAudioBusLayout<FmodAudioBusLayout>` get_audio_bus_layout() "
"static"

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:63 aa6b443dfabc4cb89e2088c2ddff2c75
msgid ""
"返回用于管理音频总线及其路由的音频总线布局。该总线布局与 Godot 的 `AudioServer`_ 总线布局同步，并提供 FMOD "
"特定的总线功能，包括 DSP 效果。"
msgstr "Returns the audio bus layout used to manage buses and routing. The layout is synchronized with Godot's `AudioServer`_ bus layout and provides FMOD-specific bus features, including DSP effects."

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:68 a918ffef846c47c7bc75996d7a8090a2
msgid ":ref:`FmodSystem<FmodSystem>` get_main_system() static"
msgstr ":ref:`FmodSystem<FmodSystem>` get_main_system() static"

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:70 11b5a2e9a3e34903aee9386d4781ff0d
msgid "返回主要的 FMOD 系统实例。这是创建声音、通道、DSP 效果和其他 FMOD 对象的主要接口。系统在服务器启动时会根据项目设置自动初始化。"
msgstr "Returns the main FMOD system instance. This is the primary interface for creating sounds, channels, DSP effects, and other FMOD objects. The system is initialized automatically from project settings when the server starts."

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:75 428b77f303874ca1bd553f68b4304f71
msgid ""
":ref:`FmodChannelGroup<FmodChannelGroup>` get_master_channel_group() "
"static"
msgstr ""
":ref:`FmodChannelGroup<FmodChannelGroup>` get_master_channel_group() "
"static"

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:77 4a40ae10f148484e9cc0aca4b293d73e
msgid "返回默认情况下所有声音通过的主通道组。它是通道组层次结构的根，可以用于控制所有正在播放声音的全局音量、音高和效果。"
msgstr "Returns the master channel group through which all sounds pass by default. It is the root of the channel group hierarchy and can control global volume, pitch, and effects for all currently playing sounds."

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:82 ffdeb8045ad944c6af540fb1433467a5
msgid "void reset_main_system(system: :ref:`FmodSystem<FmodSystem>`) static"
msgstr "void reset_main_system(system: :ref:`FmodSystem<FmodSystem>`) static"

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:84 f445d759a2884f58bee6cf3c4b7aa847
msgid "重置主 FMOD 系统实例。"
msgstr "FMOD instance."

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:89 d3256732d465495fa84f606388f31dea
msgid "FmodSystem"
msgstr "FmodSystem"

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:91 dc17f0daf5be4b9cbb06b8f07f6091a5
msgid "继承自： `RefCounted`_"
msgstr "Inherits: `RefCounted`_"

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:93 a842ef946b3e434d92c36facf2e16396
msgid "**FMOD::System 对象的包装类，提供音频系统管理和控制**"
msgstr "**FMOD::System object, provides audio manages and controls**."

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:98 3b7b4d6e22cd42be817def6fe355529f
msgid ""
"**FmodSystem** 封装了 FMOD 核心 API 的 FMOD::System "
"对象，并提供全面的音频系统管理功能。该类负责系统初始化、音频设备管理、声音创建、播放控制以及录音功能。"
msgstr "**FmodSystem** wraps the FMOD::System object from the FMOD Core API and provides comprehensive audio system management. It is responsible for system initialization, audio device management, sound creation, playback control, and recording."

#: ../../source/api_reference/core.rst:100 fd48cb585f68406fbcccde5b8bd215c1
msgid ""
"FMOD System 是 FMOD 音频引擎的核心。它管理混音器、音轨、声音、DSP 效果和输出设备。对于高级应用场景，可以创建多个 "
"**FmodSystem** 实例；对于常规应用，则可以通过 :ref:`FmodServer<FmodServer>` 使用全局单例。"
msgstr ""
"FMOD System is the core of the FMOD audio engine. It manages the mixer, "
"channels, sounds, DSP effects, and output devices. Advanced use cases can"
" create multiple **FmodSystem** instances; common projects usually use "
"the global singleton through :ref:`FmodServer<FmodServer>`."

